{"tid":1894803,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請求CDC的白宮聯署","createTime":"2020-02-24T07:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T07:35:17.000Z","uid":18482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1abbf89d9506dff5c335e86293247e1068a68e3a","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:00:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=3052dac7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以快啲簽左佢，唔好再做deadline fighter。簽完都幫我推推post。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWARS 不似預期<br />\n<br />\n醫學與科學看重證據，可是 WARS 的數據都在中共國內，而中共又把瘟疫變為政治手段，因此中共國的數據都不能盡信。<br />\n<br />\n面對問題，恐懼和逃避都太消極。惟有親自找出可信的數據。<br />\n<br />\n感謝香港還有冷靜的醫生護士，親身對香港第一名確診患者進行空氣採樣（air sampling），檢測病毒含量。結果驚人。即使病人的上呼吸道中每毫升分泌物就有一百萬個病毒（含量屬頗高至高），但病人呼吸、咳嗽或談話所噴出的空氣，也找不到 WARS 病毒（又或者是少於檢測範圍）。<br />\n<br />\n雖然這數據只基於病人，但卻比中共國先前說的氣懸體（aerosol）傳播論更實在，因為是活體數據。而從香港醫生的數據看來，WARS 主要是從飛沫傳播，其次可能是接觸傳播，至於空氣傳播基本上不可能，因為病人呼出的空氣沒有病毒。這正正就是與中共誇大的疫情相反。<br />\n<br />\n另外，這也解釋了為何傳染個案，都與聚餐有關，這不是打邊爐所獨有的霧化，而是燒烤、中餐都會傳播。因為上呼吸道分泌物的病毒含量高，口水自然能有效傳染病毒（隱性患者的病毒含量會較低）。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中共國以外地區，WARS 的嚴重患者比例低於 20%，集中於老人家，而死亡率低則於 2%。這明顯比 SARS 弱，都表明 WARS 並不如中共所說那般恐怖，只是新病毒而已（又或者是實驗室洩漏而已）。<br />\n<br />\n老實說，香港人死於 WARS 的機會，比死於中共的政治手段的機會低很多。當香港人為集中精神，乃至於精神崩潰去「抗疫」時，又有否想着把主權拿回手？又有否參與過白宮聯署邀請美國疾病管制與預防中心（CDC）協助香港？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相於氣懸體的帖文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/347501365699305/posts/857991111316992/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F347501365699305%2Fposts%2F857991111316992%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=fadce464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/347501365699305/posts/857991111316992/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n相關影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y4NWqmGSvUc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY4NWqmGSvUc&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=4c47be96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y4NWqmGSvUc</a><br />\n<br />\nCredit To: Facebook page-Bio Sciences"},{"pid":"c380fd441cfec60cb5108b6b626cb4d36139b0bd","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:00:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f524867ae0b6cc60e01915f4c7d280c86ab185b9","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:00:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2ce1a27f10950dfd95666ee2d39436f4e085ef86","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ff57e9f50f714d5cac5dfb7e4583b1c00cd676c4","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"5610d5671f99bfd713bb7d4aedaccc369a9e353b","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:01:23.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8d68c8aa39bc54e1d221e1796fa908e65e8f9d45","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"a339d44bd02f588c8594a561f1ea04783b73528d","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a41ea5cdc1aea680cbb5c4d8b4b097a1600efa88","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:02:14.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"ccdc42b6d23384a0b4a7780b72e07581b449d463","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:02:25.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"06cf40fb73431f7e2dc395a4cf96dffa3b2f2fd1","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"b14e6d483686c471412cb12c4df300f00517ceeb","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"8d7cc34294b8729dcfeea6181aaffbf5fedca67b","tid":1894803,"uid":18482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"屌10連左"},{"pid":"4a63f0f6ced55e9d38e6bf189a5169b9366cfc94","tid":1894803,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5ed469fe2733fd4b0914bb25d372e55810f81252","tid":1894803,"uid":50131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:35:17.000Z","msg":"簽ed"}]}